text: Juanita Ruth Feldhahn (born 7 June 1973) is a road cyclist from Australia. She represented her nation at the 2000 Summer Olympics in the women's road race. ==References== ==External links== * Profile at sports-reference.com Category:Australian female cyclists Category:Cyclists at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic cyclists of Australia Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Queensland Category:1973 births
